#: .\android_ears.json
msgid "Bio-Synthetic"
msgstr "生物合成體"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bio-Synthetic'}
#: .\android_ears.json
msgid ""
"You are a bio-synthetic android designed by Chi industries on the eve of the"
" Cataclysm, very few were made."
msgstr "你是大災變前夕由奇工業設計的生物合成安卓機器人，產量極少。"

#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "Chinese power armor"
msgid_plural "Chinese power armors"
msgstr[0] "中國動力裝甲"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Chinese power armor'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Chi Industries power armor'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'XEDRA excursion suit'}.
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid "The %s engages."
msgstr "%s啟動。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chinese power armor'}
#: .\gb_armor.json
msgid ""
"Developed after the groundbreaking creation of power armor by the United "
"States, the Type-13 combat exoskeleton was China's attempt at making an "
"equivalent to the United States. Development of these suits of protection "
"were significantly rushed though, and are often inferior to their American "
"counterparts, if a bit lighter to wear."
msgstr ""
"在美國開創性地研發出動力裝甲後，中國為打造與之匹敵的裝備而開發了13型戰鬥外骨骼。然而這些防護服的研發進程極為倉促，雖穿戴稍輕便，但性能通常遜於美國同類產品。"

