#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Chinese power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Chinese power armors (active)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Chi Industries power armor (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Chi Industries power armors (active)'}.
