#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid "Zhuazi N-1b"
msgid_plural "Zhuazi N-1bs"
msgstr[0] "爪子N-1b"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Zhuazi N-1b'}
#: .\gb_bots.json
msgid ""
"The Zhuazi N-1 is a unmanned ground vehicle that was rumored to exist on the"
" dark corners of internet before the Cataclysm, confirmed to be very real "
"only relatively recently. When they are not deployed, Zhuazi drones look "
"similar to large ballistic shells, and only deploy their legs after they've "
"impacted the ground after falling in a ballistic arc from beyond the "
"horizon. The mechanical feet act as spades, and are also sufficiently sharp "
"to damage any would-be assailant. The N-1b variant was designed to be more "
"versatile than its cheaper cousin, allowing it to be upgraded into a wide "
"variety of forms at Chinese drop pods."
msgstr ""
"爪子N-1是一種無人地面載具，在大災變前就傳聞存在於互聯網的黑暗角落，直到最近才被證實確實存在。當它們未部署時，爪子無人機看起來像大型彈道炮彈，只有在從地平線外以彈道弧線墜落撞擊地面後才會展開腿部。機械腳起到鏟子的作用，也足夠鋒利以傷害任何潛在攻擊者。N-1b變體設計得比其更便宜的同類更加多功能，允許其在中國空投艙中升級成多種形態。"

