"A simple bento box containing only cooked rice and a single plum, forming "
"the famous Hinomaru of Japan."
msgstr "一個簡易便當盒，僅包含米飯和一顆梅子，構成了日本著名的日之丸圖案。"

#: .\gb_food.json
msgid "bento"
msgid_plural "bento"
msgstr[0] "便當"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'bento'}
#: .\gb_food.json
msgid ""
"A bento box containing only cooked rice and a side of meat, commonly eaten "
"by Japanese citizens on the go."
msgstr "一個便當盒，包含米飯和一份肉類配菜，是日本市民外出時常吃的食物。"

#: .\gb_food.json
msgid "deluxe bento"
msgid_plural "deluxe bento"
msgstr[0] "豪華便當"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'deluxe bento'}
#: .\gb_food.json
msgid ""
"A bento box containing cooked rice, and multiple sides of meat and noodles, "
"commonly eaten by Japanese citizens on the go."
msgstr "一個便當盒，包含米飯以及多份肉類和麵條配菜，是日本市民外出時常吃的食物。"

#: .\gb_food.json
msgid "meat bento"
msgid_plural "meat bento"
msgstr[0] "肉類便當"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'meat bento'}
#: .\gb_food.json
msgid ""
"A bento box containing containing only various pieces of fried meat, "
"commonly eaten by Japanese citizens on the go."
msgstr "一個便當盒，僅包含各種炸肉塊，是日本市民外出時常吃的食物。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "Type 23 Digisword"
msgid_plural "Type 23 Digiswords"
msgstr[0] "23型數字劍"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Type 23 Digiswords (active)'}.
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "Activate"
msgstr "激活"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword'}.
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "The Digisword is activated!"
msgstr "數字劍已激活！"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword'}.
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "The Digisword's beam-edge sputters out due to lack of charge."
msgstr "數字劍的光束刃因電量不足而熄滅。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword'}
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A large sword seemingly made out of an exotic composite and oddly cheap "
"plastic. Runs off of medium batteries. Activate the Digisword to increase "
"damage outpout."
msgstr "一把看似由奇異複合材料與廉價塑料製成的大劍。使用中型電池供電。激活數字劍可提升傷害輸出。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "Type 23 Digisword (active)"
msgid_plural "Type 23 Digiswords (active)"
msgstr[0] "23型數字劍（激活狀態）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword (active)', 'str_pl': 'Type
#. 23 Digiswords (active)'}.
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "The Digisword's beam-edge deactivates."
msgstr "數字劍的光束刃已關閉。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Type 23 Digisword (active)', 'str_pl': 'Type 23
#. Digiswords (active)'}
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A large sword seemingly made out of an exotic composite and oddly cheap "
"plastic. Runs off of medium batteries. Activate the Digisword to increase "
"damage outpout. A lime-colored beam of energy hums faintly across the edge "
"of the blade."
msgstr "一把看似由奇異複合材料與廉價塑料製成的大劍。使用中型電池供電。激活數字劍可提升傷害輸出。劍刃邊緣隱約閃爍著淡綠色的能量光束。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "Type 26 Chargelance"
msgid_plural "Type 26 Chargelances"
msgstr[0] "26型充能長槍"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A state-of-the-art direct energy weapon developed by famed Japanese Robotics"
" company, Chi-Industries. The Type 26 Chargelance is a curious mixture of "
"21st century technological prowess and medieval craftsmanship. Despite "
"sporting a thermal charge cannon, the chargelance was also designed to use "
"its ponderous mass effectively in melee combat. The front of the weapon is "
"honed to a fine, cutting edge. Uses UPS charge to operate."
msgstr ""
"由日本著名機器人公司Chi-"
"Industries開發的尖端定向能量武器。26型充能長槍是21世紀科技實力與中世紀工藝的奇妙結合。儘管配備了熱充能炮，該武器也設計用於在近戰中以沉重質量有效作戰。武器前端被磨成鋒利的切割刃。使用UPS充電運作。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "Type 13 DigiBow"
msgid_plural "Type 13 DigiBows"
msgstr[0] "13型數字弓"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A modern bow designed by Chi-Industries, this weapon is an eclectic mixture "
"of modern forays into direct energy warfare and the ancient Japanese "
"tradition of Kyudo: The art of the bow. It's sleek white exterior hides an "
"immense array of laser projectors, that create a complex arrangement of "
"light to act not only as the bowstring, but the arrow as well. Uses medium "
"batteries."
msgstr ""
"由Chi-"
"Industries設計的現代弓，這件武器是現代定向能量戰探索與日本古老弓道傳統的折衷結合。其光滑的白色外殼下隱藏著大量激光投影器，能產生複雜的光線排列，不僅作為弓弦，也充當箭矢。使用中型電池。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "XEDRA Pattern AR"
msgid_plural "XEDRA Pattern ARs"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA制式突擊步槍"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A rare laser-based firearm employed by XEDRA at some point after the "
"cataclysm. Unlike most laser weapons, this firearm uses commonly-found "
"medium batteries in place of a standard magazine. The rifle seems to be "
"deliberately modelled after a M4 Carbine."
msgstr ""
"XEDRA在災變後某個時期使用的稀有激光槍械。與大多數激光武器不同，這把槍使用常見的中型電池替代標準彈匣。步槍似乎刻意模仿了M4卡賓槍的設計。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "3 rd."
msgstr "3 發"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "XEDRA pattern thermal magnum"
msgid_plural "XEDRA pattern thermal magnums"
msgstr[0] "XEDRA制式熱能手槍"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"A rare laser-based firearm employed by XEDRA at some point after the "
"cataclysm. Unlike most laser weapons, this firearm uses commonly-found light"
" batteries in place of a standard magazine. The pistol seems to be "
"deliberately modelled after a large caliber revolver."
msgstr ""
"XEDRA在災變後某個時期使用的稀有激光槍械。與大多數激光武器不同，這把槍使用常見的輕型電池替代標準彈匣。手槍似乎刻意模仿了大口徑左輪手槍的設計。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "esoteric electronic device"
msgid_plural "esoteric electronic devices"
msgstr[0] "深奧的電子設備"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'esoteric electronic device'}
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"This is a rare electronic device of an unknown purpose, it seems valuable."
msgstr "這是一種用途不明的稀有電子設備，看起來很有價值。"

#: .\gb_items.json
msgid "synthetic bio-flesh"
msgid_plural "synthetic bio-fleshs"
msgstr[0] "合成生物肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'synthetic bio-flesh'}
#: .\gb_items.json
msgid ""
"This is a scrap of synthetic bio-flesh. These were cultured in labs on an "
"industrial scale before the cataclysm for use in bio-synth robots. Even the "
"slightly electrical impusle can make this scrap of black, rubbery biomass "
"twitch and dance in your hands."
msgstr ""
"這是一塊合成生物肉。在災變前，這些肉曾在實驗室中大規模培養，用於生物合成機器人。即使是微弱的電脈衝，也能讓這塊黑色、橡膠般的生物質在你手中抽搐舞動。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Salamander Mk.1"
msgid_plural "Salamander Mk.1s"
msgstr[0] "蠑螈 Mk.1"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Salamander Mk.1'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"For years, various defense contractors and roboticists puzzled over one "
"simple question: what is the best form of locomotion for large robotic "
"vehicle? Various methods of movement were suggested until one Boston "
"Dynamics engineer suggested eschewing electro-mechanical treads or wheels in"
" favor of bio-synethic legs. The Salamander Mk.I was his brainchild: large "
"bipedal hybrid robots used as a form of riot control by law enforcement."
msgstr ""
"多年來，各種國防承包商和機器人專家一直為一個簡單問題所困擾：大型機器人載具的最佳移動形式是什麼？人們提出了多種移動方式，直到一位波士頓動力公司的工程師建議摒棄機電履帶或車輪，轉而採用生物合成腿。蠑螈"
" Mk.I 便是他的創意：一種大型雙足混合機器人，被執法部門用於防暴控制。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken Salamander Mk.1"
msgid_plural "broken Salamander Mk.1s"
msgstr[0] "損壞的蠑螈 Mk.1"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Salamander Mk.1'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Salamander Mk.2'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Salamander Mk.3'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A broken Salamander, now wrecked and motionless. Synthetic blood still oozes"
" from its muscular legs. It could be gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一臺損壞的蠑螈，現已殘破且靜止不動。合成血液仍從其肌肉發達的雙腿中滲出。可以將其拆解以獲取零件。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Salamander Mk.2"
msgid_plural "Salamander Mk.2s"
msgstr[0] "蠑螈 Mk.2"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Salamander Mk.2'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"After the Salamander Mk.1's success in law enforcement and riot suppression "
"trials, the bio-synthetic design piqued the interest of the US military. "
"This variant of the Salamander was originally designed for use in Middle "
"Eastern combat zones, but soon saw heavy use in America."
msgstr ""
"在蠑螈 Mk.1 於執法和防暴鎮壓試驗中取得成功後，這種生物合成設計引起了美國軍方的興趣。這款蠑螈變體最初設計用於中東戰區，但很快在美國得到了廣泛應用。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken Salamander Mk.2"
msgid_plural "broken Salamander Mk.2s"
msgstr[0] "損壞的蠑螈 Mk.2"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Salamander Mk.3"
msgid_plural "Salamander Mk.3s"
msgstr[0] "蠑螈 Mk.3"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Salamander Mk.3'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"After the Salamander Mk.1's success in law enforcement and riot suppression "
"trials, the bio-synthetic design piqued the interest of the US military. "
"This variant of the Salamander was originally designed for use in Middle "
"Eastern combat zones, but soon saw heavy use in America. This variant has "
"received in upgrade in the form of a CROWS turret armed with a 5.56x45mm "
"caliber machinegun."
msgstr ""
"在蠑螈 Mk.1 "
"於執法和防暴鎮壓試驗中取得成功後，這種生物合成設計引起了美國軍方的興趣。這款蠑螈變體最初設計用於中東戰區，但很快在美國得到了廣泛應用。此型號已升級，配備了一挺"
" 5.56x45mm 口徑機槍的 CROWS 炮塔。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "CRACK!!"
msgstr "咔嚓！！"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken Salamander Mk.3"
msgid_plural "broken Salamander Mk.3s"
msgstr[0] "損壞的蠑螈 Mk.3"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Wraitheon PDW"
msgid_plural "Wraitheon PDWs"
msgstr[0] "雷神心理防禦武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Wraitheon PDW'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Designed and produced in the months leading up to mass unrest in New "
"England, the Wraitheon Psychological Defense Weapon is perhaps one of the "
"stranger weapons in the employ of the United States Military. A derivative "
"of the more famous microwave Active Denial System, the Wraitheon "
"Psychological Defense System uses a complex series of audio-visual signals "
"to induce a state of extreme discomfort in the wearer. How effective these "
"weapon platforms were remains unknown."
msgstr ""
"在新英格蘭大規模騷亂爆發前的幾個月裡設計和生產的雷神心理防禦武器，或許是美軍裝備中較為奇特的武器之一。作為更著名的微波主動拒止系統的衍生品，雷神心理防禦系統使用一系列複雜的視聽信號，誘導穿戴者進入極度不適的狀態。這些武器平臺的實際效果如何，至今仍是個謎。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken Wraitheon PDW"
msgid_plural "broken Wraitheon PDWs"
msgstr[0] "損壞的雷神心理防禦武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Wraitheon PDW'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A broken Wraitheon Psychological Defense Weapon. It could be gutted for "
"spare parts."
msgstr "一臺損壞的雷神心理防禦武器。可以將其拆解以獲取零件。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Bullfrog Relief System"
msgid_plural "Bullfrog Relief Systems"
msgstr[0] "牛蛙救援系統"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bullfrog Relief System'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Originally designed for use in disaster relief zones with uneven terrain "
"that normal vehicles couldn't even hope to negotiate. The Bullfrog relief "
"system is a curious sight in contemporary New England. They were not "
"designed with any hostile intent in mind, and the military had no use for a "
"three-legged robot that would do little more than haul away rubble from a "
"collapsed building. Why exactly these once-docile machines are hostile is "
"anyone's guess."
msgstr ""
"最初設計用於地形崎嶇、普通車輛難以通行的救災區域。牛蛙救援系統在當代新英格蘭是一道奇特的風景。它們的設計初衷並非敵對，軍方也對這種除了從倒塌建築中拖走瓦礫外幾乎別無他用的三足機器人不感興趣。這些曾經溫順的機器為何變得具有敵意，誰也說不清。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken Bullfrog Relief System"
msgid_plural "broken Bullfrog Relief Systems"
msgstr[0] "損壞的牛蛙救援系統"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken Bullfrog Relief System'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A broken Bullfrog Reliev System, now wrecked and motionless. It could be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一臺損壞的牛蛙救援系統，現已殘破且靜止不動。可以將其拆解以獲取零件。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Incidi-tank"
msgid_plural "Incidi-tanks"
msgstr[0] "焚化坦克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Incidi-tank'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A post cataclysm tank design made by a seemingly unknown group of people "
"with immense technical knowledge, this design is made for one purpose only: "
"purging what lies in its front with burning gasoline. Might explode when "
"killed."
msgstr "一種由一群似乎身份不明但擁有深厚技術知識的人在災變後設計的坦克，其設計目的只有一個：用燃燒的汽油淨化前方的一切。被摧毀時可能會爆炸。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Broken Incidi-tank"
msgid_plural "Broken Incidi-tanks"
msgstr[0] "損壞的焚化坦克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Broken Incidi-tank'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Broken Police Compliance Drone'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "A broken Incindi-Tank. It could be gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一臺損壞的焚化坦克。可以將其拆解以獲取零件。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Police Compliance Drone"
msgid_plural "Police Compliance Drones"
msgstr[0] "警方合規無人機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Police Compliance Drone'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"The larger cousin of the pestersome eyebot, the Western Dynamics Police "
"Compliance Drone is a far more serious threat. Approximately the size of a "
"large couch, this flying vessel seeks to retain law and order as specified "
"by New England Police before the Cataclysm."
msgstr ""
"作為惱人的眼球機器人的大型近親，西部動力警方合規無人機是一個更為嚴重的威脅。這架飛行器大約有一個大沙發那麼大，旨在按照災變前新英格蘭警方的規定維持法律與秩序。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "Broken Police Compliance Drone"
msgid_plural "Broken Police Compliance Drones"
msgstr[0] "損壞的警方合規無人機"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "ZTK-34"
msgid_plural "ZTK-34s"
msgstr[0] "ZTK-34"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ZTK-34'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid ""
"The ZTK-34 is considered the pinnacle of unmanned Chinese military "
"technology before the Cataclysm. Originally, it was intended for use along "
"the long and often uninhabted frontier between China and Russia along the "
"Manchurian plane, this variant somehow found its way to New England in "
"recent times. It is extremely heavily armored, and features a 120mm "
"Autocannon capable of defeating virtually any threat."
msgstr ""
"ZTK-34被視為大災變前中國無人軍事技術的巔峰之作。原本設計用於中俄邊境滿洲平原漫長且人煙稀少的防線，但這一型號不知何故在近期流落到了新英格蘭地區。它擁有極其厚重的裝甲，並配備一門120毫米自動炮，足以擊潰幾乎任何威脅。"

#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "broken ZTK-34"
msgid_plural "broken ZTK-34s"
msgstr[0] "損壞的ZTK-34"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken ZTK-34'}
#: .\gb_mobs.json
msgid "A broken ZTK-34. It could be gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一臺損壞的ZTK-34。可以拆解獲取備用零件。"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chi Industries Salesman"
msgstr "奇工業銷售員"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chi Industries Saleswoman"
msgstr "奇工業女銷售員"

#. ~ Profession (male Chi Industries Salesman) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm you were a sales representaive for the Japanese "
"robotics company, Chi industries. Working in the sales division of a Chi "
"Industries office outside of Boston was of great interest to you, but any "
"communication from the corporate leadership went mysteriously silent in "
"Tokyo days before civil order collapsed."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你曾是日本機器人公司奇工業的銷售代表。在波士頓郊外的奇工業辦事處銷售部門工作讓你充滿熱情，但就在社會秩序崩潰前幾天，東京總部的所有聯絡卻神秘地中斷了。"

#. ~ Profession (female Chi Industries Saleswoman) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm you were a sales representaive for the Japanese "
"robotics company, Chi industries. Working in the sales division of a Chi "
"Industries office outside of Boston was of great interest to you, but any "
"communication from the corporate leadership went mysteriously silent in "
"Tokyo days before civil order collapsed."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你曾是日本機器人公司奇工業的銷售代表。在波士頓郊外的奇工業辦事處銷售部門工作讓你充滿熱情，但就在社會秩序崩潰前幾天，東京總部的所有聯絡卻神秘地中斷了。"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chi Industries Employee"
msgstr "奇工業員工"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chi Industries Employee"
msgstr "奇工業員工"

#. ~ Profession (male Chi Industries Employee) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm you were a low level employee for the Japanese robotics"
" company, Chi industries. Working as an employee at a local branch allowed "
"you to learn a bit about the inner workings of the famed company's consumer "
"products and gynoids. Hopefully it comes in handy during the cataclysm."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你是日本機器人公司奇工業的一名基層員工。在當地分支機構的工作讓你對這家知名公司的消費產品和女性機器人有了一些瞭解。希望這些知識能在大災變中派上用場。"

#. ~ Profession (female Chi Industries Employee) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm you were a low level employee for the Japanese robotics"
" company, Chi industries. Working as an employee at a local branch allowed "
"you to learn a bit about the inner workings of the famed company's consumer "
"products and gynoids. Hopefully it comes in handy during the cataclysm."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你是日本機器人公司奇工業的一名基層員工。在當地分支機構的工作讓你對這家知名公司的消費產品和女性機器人有了一些瞭解。希望這些知識能在大災變中派上用場。"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chi Industries Enthusiast"
msgstr "奇工業愛好者"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chi Industries Enthusiast"
msgstr "奇工業愛好者"

#. ~ Profession (male Chi Industries Enthusiast) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
