#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chi Industries Operative"
msgstr "奇工業特工"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chi Industries Operative"
msgstr "奇工業特工"

#. ~ Profession (male Chi Industries Operative) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You used your background in the security industry to get a job as a high-"
"level security operative working for the more shadowy interests of famed "
"Japanese android concern, Chi Industries. You were given a somewhat "
"extensive suite of augmentations, hopefully those can help you against the "
"new threats that this world has to offer."
msgstr ""
"你利用安保行業的背景，在知名日本機器人企業奇工業的隱秘部門擔任高級安全特工。你獲得了一套相當全面的強化改造，希望這些能幫助你應對這個世界湧現的新威脅。"

#. ~ Profession (female Chi Industries Operative) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You used your background in the security industry to get a job as a high-"
"level security operative working for the more shadowy interests of famed "
"Japanese android concern, Chi Industries. You were given a somewhat "
"extensive suite of augmentations, hopefully those can help you against the "
"new threats that this world has to offer."
msgstr ""
"你利用安保行業的背景，在知名日本機器人企業奇工業的隱秘部門擔任高級安全特工。你獲得了一套相當全面的強化改造，希望這些能幫助你應對這個世界湧現的新威脅。"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Scrapper Scav"
msgstr "拾荒者"

#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Scrapper Scav"
msgstr "拾荒者"

#. ~ Profession (male Scrapper Scav) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were a pretty normal person before the cataclysm, but all that changed "
"when your basic hiearchy of needs changed from dealing with paychecks and "
"internet to scrounging for food. You began to learn the ropes of foraging "
"through the unsafe wilds of what were once nice neighboorhods, and "
"eventually came within the protective aegis of a scrapper community."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你本是個普通人，但當你的基本需求從應付工資和網絡變成搜尋食物時，一切都變了。你開始在曾是宜人社區的危險荒野中學習覓食之道，最終受到一個拾荒者社區的庇護。"

#. ~ Profession (female Scrapper Scav) description
#: .\gkb_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were a pretty normal person before the cataclysm, but all that changed "
"when your basic hiearchy of needs changed from dealing with paychecks and "
"internet to scrounging for food. You began to learn the ropes of foraging "
"through the unsafe wilds of what were once nice neighboorhods, and "
"eventually came within the protective aegis of a scrapper community."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你本是個普通人，但當你的基本需求從應付工資和網絡變成搜尋食物時，一切都變了。你開始在曾是宜人社區的危險荒野中學習覓食之道，最終受到一個拾荒者社區的庇護。"

